					<div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="150" height="150" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;150&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20150&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-pin-media="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-19.jpg" data-pin-title="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" data-pin-description="This Lemon Olive Oil Cake is sunshine in every slice. Moist, zesty, and effortlessly elegant, one bite will brighten your day." class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-19-150x150.jpg" /></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="150" height="150" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;150&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20150&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-pin-media="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-18.jpg" data-pin-title="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" data-pin-description="This Lemon Olive Oil Cake is sunshine in every slice. Moist, zesty, and effortlessly elegant, one bite will brighten your day." alt="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-18-150x150.jpg" /></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="150" height="150" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;150&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20150&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-pin-media="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-17.jpg" data-pin-title="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" data-pin-description="This Lemon Olive Oil Cake is sunshine in every slice. Moist, zesty, and effortlessly elegant, one bite will brighten your day." alt="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-17-150x150.jpg" /></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="150" height="150" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;150&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20150&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-pin-media="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-19-1.jpg" data-pin-title="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" data-pin-description="This Lemon Olive Oil Cake is sunshine in every slice. Moist, zesty, and effortlessly elegant, one bite will brighten your day." alt="Hamburger Gravy" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-19-1-150x150.jpg" /></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="150" height="150" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;150&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20150&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-pin-media="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-20.jpg" data-pin-title="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" data-pin-description="This Lemon Olive Oil Cake is sunshine in every slice. Moist, zesty, and effortlessly elegant, one bite will brighten your day." alt="Hamburger Gravy" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-20-150x150.jpg" /></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="150" height="150" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;150&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20150&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-pin-media="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-16.jpg" data-pin-title="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" data-pin-description="This Lemon Olive Oil Cake is sunshine in every slice. Moist, zesty, and effortlessly elegant, one bite will brighten your day." alt="Lemon Olive Oil Cake" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner  dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-single perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-16-150x150.jpg" /></div><span id="dpsp-post-content-markup" data-image-pin-it="true"></span>
<p>When life gives you lemons, make this Lemon Olive Oil Cake.</p>



<p>I know what you're thinking. No, this cake has no weird olive oil flavor. Yes, it's made with fruity olive oil instead of butter, but that only makes this Mediterranean cake wonderfully tender and moist for days.</p>



<p>Taste-wise, it's bright, fresh, and citrus, especially with that sweet-tart lemon glaze drizzled on top.</p>



<p>And can we talk about the presentation? It looks like something you’d serve at a party.</p>



<p>Serve it with a cup of tea or coffee, and you’ve got the perfect afternoon treat: moist, zesty, and effortlessly elegant.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-perfmatters-preload decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" src="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-6.jpg" alt="Glazed lemon olive oil cake, surrounded by fresh lemons and a slice served on a plate." class="wp-image-8761640" srcset="https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-6.jpg 1200w, https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-6-200x300.jpg 200w, https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-6-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-6-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://insanelygoodrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lemon-Olive-Oil-Cake-6-750x1125.jpg 750w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" fetchpriority="high"></figure><div class='code-block code-block-1' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
